FRONTEND COMPONENTS

1. Main Dashboard Layout
- Header with app title and logout button
- Search bar with real-time filtering
- Filter dropdown (by mediator, period, status)
- Import/Export buttons (top-right)
- Data table (main content area)
- Client details sidebar (collapsible)

2. Client Table Component
// Required features:
- Sortable columns (name, date, amounts)
- Pagination (20 items per page)
- Row click opens sidebar
- Highlight selected row
- Loading states
- Empty state message

3. Client Sidebar Component
// Display sections:
- Client basic info (name, ID)
- Financial overview (grid layout)
- Times scheduled counter
- Remarks history (scrollable)
- Add/Edit remark form
- Schedule session button
- Close sidebar button

4. Admin Dashboard
// Features:
- Separate route (/admin)
- Mediator CRUD table
- Client manual entry form
- System statistics cards
- Access control (admin role only)

5. Login Interface Design
// Requirements:
 - Minimal login form (email + password)
 - Proper error handling (display backend errors, invalid credentials, and validation issues)
 - Simple "Login" button
 - Loading state for submission
 - Success redirects to dashboard on valid login
 - If already logged in, auto-redirect to dashboard
 - No registration or password reset (admin-controlled users only)
 - Show generic error for unexpected issues, specific feedback for validation/login errors